<title>UK: UK's Provident says good 1997 start maintained.</title>
<headline>UK's Provident says good 1997 start maintained.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>British credit and insurance group Provident Financial Plc said on Thursday the good start the company made to trading in 1997 has been maintained.</p>
<p>&quot;(The good start) has been maintained and the trends, which have been reported previously (in the 1996 annual report) have remained largely unchanged during the first quarter,&quot; chairman Antony Warde-Norbury said in a statement.</p>
